<template>

  <m-warning-notify
    v-if="showWarningNotify"
    :closeWarningFunction="onCloseWarningNotify"
  ></m-warning-notify>
  <m-exclamation
    v-if="showExclamation"
    :closeExclamationFunction="onCloseExclamation"
  ></m-exclamation>
</template>
<script>
export default {
  name: "MisaDialog",
  props: ["closeFunction"],
  methods: {
    onShowWarningNotify() {
      this.showWarningNotify = true;
    },
    onShowExclamation() {
      this.showExclamation = true;
    },
    onCloseWarningNotify() {
      this.showWarningNotify = false;
    },
    onCloseExclamation() {
      this.showExclamation = false;
    },
  },
  data() {
    return {
      showWarningNotify: false,
      showExclamation: false,
    };
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
